Release Info:
 WRC Powerslide is the brand new game, developed by Milestone, which mixes
 amazing and exciting gameplay elements in one game. With a colorful and
 smart style, this new title offer the chance to try all the WRC licensed
 elements with an arcade attitude.

We're currently looking for...

Notes:

2) Put (via FTP) EP4356-NPEB01324_00-WRCARCADEKEY0000.edat in:
   dev_hdd0/home/0000000?/exdata/
   If you don't have exdata dir just create it manually and put
   the .edat inside.

Tested on CFW 4.30

Enjoy
